  "time_ut": 1656647757,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0da2\u0dba\u0dda \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0da9 \u0dc0\u0dbd\u0da7 \u0dad\u0dc0\u0db8\u0dad\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dba\u0da7 3\u0d9a\u0d9c\u0dda \u0d85\u0db1\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dba",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "3 percent still approve of government jobs",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The information for the month of June of the island-wide referendum on 'How the Country Thinks' conducted by Veritas Research has been released.",
        "According to the results of the survey, public approval for government work is around 3%. Last January, when the survey was conducted, the level was 10%.",
        "Are you satisfied with the way things are going in the country? The referendum also noted that for the month of June, 2% of the population was satisfied with the way things were going in the country. In January, the figure was 6%.",
        "The economy is expected to have a negative 96 (-96) in June. Multicolor queries were used to perform this evaluation, and the response to those queries was rated from negative 100 (-100) to positive 100 (+100).",
        "According to this austerity, a full +100 value is obtained only if everyone believes that the economy is in good shape and that it is turning for the better. On the other hand, a full-100 value is obtained if everyone believes that the economy is in bad shape, and that it is getting worse.",
        "Intermediate responses depend on the size of the response, and a positive value above 0 means that the more people have a good idea of \u200b\u200bthe economy. Here, only 1.8% said the economy was doing well. 1.3% said the economy was recovering. No one has said that the economy is doing well. Confidence in the economy stood at a negative 83 (-83) in January.",
        "The Gallup Institute of America, titled Mood of the Nation, has adapted the questions and calculations used to poll the country's public opinion to suit Sri Lanka. The specialty of this system is to be able to question the entire public opinion of a country through a representative sample of the people living all over the country. Verity Research used a sample of 1052 people who satisfied this fact. Vanguard Survey (Private) has supported data collection."
      ],
